'''Sam Uche Anyamele''', ni umukinnyi wa sinema yo muri [[Nigeriya]]<ref>https://www.tmznaija.com/2021/01/sam-uche-anyamele-actor-and-former.html?m=1</ref>. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Anyamele yavukiye Isolo, muri Lagos nk'imfura mu muryango hamwe na barumuna batandatu: abahungu batatu n'abakobwa batatu.<ref>https://www.nigeriafilms.com/movie-news/76-behind-the-scene/7840-i-m-not-as-bad-as-people-think-sam-uche-anyamele</ref> Yarangije amashuri abanza mu ishuri ribanza rya Faronbi Isolo (1988 kugeza 1993) no mu gace ka Ukwa k'ubutegetsi bw'ibanze muri Leta ya Abia nyuma aza kwiga mu ishuri ry'ikibonezamvugo rya Isolo (1993 kugeza 1999)<ref>https://irokotv.com/actors/1291/sam-uche-anyamele</ref>. Yarangije icyiciro cya mbere mu burezi bw’ubucuruzi mu 2007 n’iyamamaza n’icyiciro cya kabiri cya kaminuza mu kuzamura imiyoborere muri 2009 muri kaminuza ya Lagos<ref>https://guardian.ng/saturday-magazine/its-osarhieme-for-actor-sam-uche-anyamele/</ref> . Yashakanye n'umukunzi umaze igihe, Osarhieme Edokpolor, aho ubukwe bwizihije ahitwa Off Ugbor Village Road muri GRA<ref>https://guardian.ng/saturday-magazine/its-osarhieme-for-actor-sam-uche-anyamele/</ref> .  

== Umwuga ==
Yakundaga gucuranga ibikoresho bya muzika mu Itorero ry'Inteko y'Imana. Mu 2004, yagaragaye kuri tereviziyo ya mbere hamwe ninkuru ya Wale Adenuga '', No pain No Gain''<ref>https://allnews.ng/tag/sam-uche-anyamele</ref>''.'' . Mu mwaka wa 2006, yatsindiye igihembo cya Afurika Movie Academy Academy (AMAA) ku bakinnyi bafite ibyiringiro byinshi kubera uruhare mu ''munsi w’impongano'' .<ref>https://www.myheritage.com/research/record-10182-2687928/sam-uche-anyamele-in-biographical-summaries-of-notable-people</ref>   Yakoze kandi nk'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyirahamwe ry'igihugu ry'abakora umwuga wo gukina ibihangano bya [[Nigeriya]]. 

Muri 2019, Anyamele yagizwe ambasaderi w’ikirango cya Max Garden Estate<ref>https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2010512-sam-uche-anyamele</ref>.  Nyuma muri uwo mwaka, yatangajwe ko yakiriye Mykmary Fashion Show yabaye ku ya 31 Kanama 2019<ref>https://www.vanguardngr.com/2019/08/actor-sam-uche-to-host-mykmary-fashion-show-2019/</ref>. 

